<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay8 />你聽說了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再過不久，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="33" />上
就要舉辦第一場活動，<delay8 />大家都在討論這件事喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay8 />不曉得會是什麼內容耶？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該不需要<delay8 />特別準備什麼吧！？<10_4 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經迫不及待啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天終於<delay8 />就是活動的日子啦！<delay20 />
是<tag a="110" b="33" /><delay8 />第一次辦活動呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />有這種活動<delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太棒了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經感受到<delay8 />
島上開始熱鬧起來啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說這個禮拜六<delay8 />就是釣魚大會了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我釣魚的技術<delay8 />沒有很好，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但凡是測試實力的比賽，我可不會缺席！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你也要參加，<delay8 />勸你別大意喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不然我可要趁你發呆的時候，<delay8 />
把魚全都釣光光啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是<delay8 />釣魚大會了啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真讓人興奮呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然垂下釣魚線、<delay8 />靜靜等魚上鉤<delay20 />
其實不符合我的性子啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但釣到大魚時的<delay8 />
那種愉悅<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在讓人欲罷不能啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說這週六<delay8 />就是捕蟲大會了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我不是什麼<delay8 />捕蟲高手，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但若要測試實力，<delay8 />我就算不願意也會拼了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說你也打算要參加嗎？<delay frames="40" />
既然這樣，<delay8 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />我們就來比看看<delay8 />
誰抓的昆蟲比較多吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 />明天就是捕蟲大會啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是期待呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />不過<delay8 />我們可得小心，<delay20 />
別抓蟲抓得太投入，<delay8 />
不小心踩到花囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />話說明天不就是<delay20 />
快樂家協會的<delay8 />審查日子嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說，我對房間有自己的一套堅持，<delay20 />
也沒道理聽別人講東講西的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我應該還是會打掃一下吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經看過<delay20 />
快樂家協會的審查結果了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的房間啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />差～不多<delay8 />就是那個樣子吧！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以某種層面來說，能用分數知道<delay20 />
別人覺得自己的房間布置得如何，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還挺有意思的呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">想不到今年也再過沒幾天就要結束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一年真的是轉眼間就過啦！ <pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />31號是今年的最後一天，<delay20 />
就用跨年倒數來向<tag a="90" b="27" />年隆重道別吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />得從現在就拿出幹勁才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />過了明天，<tag a="90" b="27" />年也要結束啦！<delay frames="40" />
新的一年終於就快要開始了呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的最後一晚，我要在廣場上跨年倒數！<delay frames="40" />
大家一起盛大慶祝，<delay8 />
迎接新年的到來吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">聽說<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />為了迎接5月1日的勞動節，<delay20 />
<colour id="3" /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="65535" />好像正在籌畫著什麼喔！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然詳情我也不清楚，<delay20 />但應該是
準備在某個離島上<delay8 />舉辦活動吧！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人感到興奮呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是勞動節了呢！<delay frames="40" />
讓我想想看，應該怎麼做，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才能前往活動會場所在的離島<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 />我記得需要<colour id="1" />勞動節旅行券<colour id="65535" />。
<delay20 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是要去哪裡才能取得呢<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天去問問<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>